      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAVANNA BEACH (7) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led throughout to score when a 3 length winner (29.86) over 520m at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Well placed and will be tough to beat. EXTREME TENSION (2) placed three back at this track then out of the placings last couple but moves to box 2 this time where he has performed well. Can improve sharply here. ZIPPING LEE (1) was well off top last time, finishing 6th (25.75) in a OPEN at Q Lakeside. Has a strong winning record here at this journey including six wins. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from two starts. Should be thereabouts. CRAB POT (4) must be respected at his pet track and distance.",
